seo: 杀软识别,进程名,反病毒软件,安全防护,插件
seo_en: antivirus detection, process name, antivirus software, security protection, plugin
summary: 该插件用于识别系统中运行的杀毒软件及其相关进程，通过匹配进程名称来检测对应的杀毒软件或安全工具。
summary_en: This plugin is used to identify antivirus software and related processes running on the system by matching process names to detect corresponding antivirus software or security tools.
